Archdocumentalist generates wiki snapshots for a specific language.
The snapshot is a collection of html pages which are indexed in index.html.

USAGE:

archdocumentalist LANGUAGE PATH

DEPENDANCES:
perl
perl-json-xs
perl-libwww


ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS
This script is based on the Sergej Pupykin's idea 
http://www.archlinux.org/packages/community/any/arch-wiki-docs/

